values: If an area of land is rugged, then it is rocky and difficult to travel through.
Their car couldn’t make it far along the rugged roads.
adj. （地面，地形）高低不平的，崎岖的；（男人的外貌）粗犷而英俊的；强健而坚毅的；（机器或其他制造品）坚固耐用的；艰难的，严峻的
